espond.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20he's%20starting%20to%20come%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20testimony%20may%20be%20used%20by%20prosecutors%20to%20support%20an%20obstruction%20of%20justice%20allegation%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20racketeering%20charge%20against%20Combs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220857ba69-ea74-4314-8ba3-8c5fe77c401a%5C%22%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bcoolest%20alien%20rockstar%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20cross-examination%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mia%20was%20asked%20why%20she%20never%20spoke%20out%20about%20Combs'%20alleged%20abuses%2C%20and%20why%20she%20instead%20posted%20dozens%20of%20glowing%20messages%20about%20him%20on%20Instagram%20throughout%20her%20nine%20years%20working%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYOU%20ARE%20THE%20COOLEST%20ALIEN%20ROCKSTAR%20UNICORN%20PIZZA%20SLICE%20AND%20WE%20FUCKING%20LOVVVVVE%20YOU!%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20her%20Instagram%20in%20a%202016%20happy%20birthday%20message%2C%20one%20of%20dozens%20shown%20to%20jurors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMia%20explained%20that%20Combs%20had%20good%20moments%20and%20good%20days.%20Keeping%20him%20happy%20and%20celebrating%20him%20online%20was%20part%20of%20her%20job%2C%20and%20also%20in%20her%20own%20best%20interest%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20things%20were%20good%2C%20you%20felt%20really%20safe%20and%20you%20almost%20forgot%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20bad%20times%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20lawyer%20Brian%20Steel%20asked%20how%20she%20could%20%26quot%3Bforget%26quot%3B%20the%20rape%20she%20alleged%20Combs%20had%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20too%20hard%20to%20think%20about%20it%2C%20so%20you%20don't%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20have%20time%20to%2C%20anyway%2C%20and%20you%20just%20want%20it%20to%20go%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteel%20kept%20pressing%20the%20point%20%E2%80%94%20why%20did%20she%20stay%20silent%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20young%20and%20manipulated%20and%20just%20eager%20to%2