0and%20sweepstakes%20to%20win%20tickets%20for%20Disney%20Cruises%20or%20tickets%20to%20Disney%20movie%20premieres.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20first%20began%20testing%20limited-edition%20perks%20for%20its%20streaming%20customers%20in%20December%202023%20and%20launched%20its%20permanent%20program%20this%20week.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20launching%20Hulu%20Perks%20in%20early%20June%2C%20though%20that%20program%20is%20currently%20only%20slated%20for%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Disney%20employee%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20Disney%2B%20Perks%20program%20said%20the%20objective%20is%20to%20keep%20streaming%20subscribers%20engaged%2C%20happy%2C%20and%20paying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20employee%20said%20preventing%20cancellations%20is%20a%20top%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChurn%20is%20just%20top%20of%20mind%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20the%20streaming%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20churn%20rate%20fell%20to%203%25%20in%20April%2C%20according%20to%20the%20subscription%20data%20firm%20Antenna.%20That%20was%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%20last%20June%20and%20only%20slightly%20above%20industry%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-chart-win-back-canceled-subscribers-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix's%202%25%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20the%20higher%20end%20of%20the%20scale%20are%20niche%20services%20like%20Apple%20TV%2B%20and%20Starz%20at%207%25%20and%208%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Disney%20spokesperson%20referred%20Business%20Insider%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-63PRE6crMg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20announcing%20the%20perks%20program%20when%20asked%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8fd47db-a627-423e-a878-609e9d1dab4c%5C%22%3EDisney%20hopes%20perks%20set%20its%20streamers%20apart%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.