ariffs-us-trading-partners-economy-stocks-markets-options-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELiberation%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Costco%20brought%20in%20some%20merchandise%20for%20summer%20earlier%20than%20usual%20and%20purchased%20more%20US-made%20inventory%2C%20CEO%20Ron%20Vachris%20said%20during%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20also%20rerouted%20some%20goods%20it%20had%20already%20purchased%20for%20its%20US%20stores%20to%20its%20locations%20abroad%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20paying%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-appeals-court-has-temporarily-reinstated-trumps-tariffs-business-lawsuit-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etariffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco's%20buyers%20have%20looked%20at%20specific%20items%20to%20figure%20out%20whether%20it%20can%20source%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-made-in-usa-american-brands-domestic-manufacturing-benefits-challenges-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS-made%20alternatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20suddenly%20more-expensive%20imports%2C%20Vachris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20it%20something%20that%20we%20can%20replace%20with%20something%20domestically%20here%2C%20or%20is%20it%20something%20that%20we%20need%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20move%20on%20quickly%20and%20bring%20in%20prior%20to%20any%20future%20tariff%20increases%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigher%20costs%20for%20some%20grocery%20staples%2C%20namely%20butter%20and%20eggs%2C%20also%20provided%20a%20challenge%20for%20Costco%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20Besides%20being%20common%20purchases%20for%20Costco%20customers%2C%20those%20two%20items%20have%20a%20large%20%26quot%3Bhalo%20effect%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20costs%20of%20other%20goods%20that%20require%20them%20as%20ingredients%2C%20Vachris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco's%20buyers%20talk%20to%20vendors%20regularly%20about%20lowering%20costs%2C%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B