ment%20at%205%3A30%20AM%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20many%20lives%20Saji%20has%20touched%2C%20one%20story%20stands%20out.%20Aasim%20Velimanna%2C%20a%20differently-abled%20rights%20activist%20and%20motivational%20speaker%2C%20is%20now%20also%20a%20swimmer%20%E2%80%94%20thanks%20to%20Saji%E2%80%99s%20quiet%20persistence%20and%20belief%20in%20his%20potential.%20For%20two%20years%2C%20Saji%20gently%20built%20trust%20with%20Aasim%E2%80%99s%20parents%2C%20reassuring%20them%20that%20their%20son%20could%20safely%20learn%20to%20swim.%20When%20they%20finally%20agreed%2C%20he%20trained%20Aasim%20not%20just%20to%20float%20or%20paddle%2C%20but%20to%20cross%20the%20river.%20It%20was%20a%20powerful%20moment%2C%20not%20just%20for%20Aasim%20but%20for%20everyone%20who%20watched%20him%20break%20through%20perceived%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20river%20has%20seen%20many%20such%20milestones.%20One%20of%20Saji%E2%80%99s%20young%20students%20even%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Asian%20Book%20of%20Records%20for%20completing%20the%20longest%20solo%20open%20sea%20swim%20by%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20born%20not%20of%20ambition%20alone%2C%20but%20of%20the%20joyful%2C%20disciplined%20training%20nurtured%20here%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%205%3A30%20AM%20every%20morning%2C%20a%20quiet%20hum%20of%20excitement%20fills%20the%20air%20as%20the%20community%20gathers.%20Children%2C%20parents%2C%20elders%20all%20assemble%20along%20the%20water%E2%80%99s%20edge.%20Saji%20begins%20with%20gentle%20stretches%20and%20simple%20exercises%2C%20weaving%20in%20warmth%20and%20joy%20with%20stories%20and%20playful%20games.%20He%20turns%20safety%20drills%20into%20moments%20of%20fun%2C%20asking%20children%20if%20they%20know%20how%20to%20find%20their%20way%20home%2C%20encouraging%20impromptu%20performances%2C%20filling%20the%20air%20with%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20rises%2C%20it%20casts%20its%20glow%20on%20a%20riverbank%20filled%20with%20smiling%2C%20spirited%20faces%2C%20re