f%20plastic%20waste%20annually%2C%20much%20of%20it%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%20or%20choking%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20not%20everyone%20sees%20plastic%20as%20the%20villain.%20%E2%80%9CPlastic%2C%20for%20me%2C%20is%20not%20a%20bad%20material%3B%20it%20is%20the%20poor%20disposal%20and%20not%20repurposing%20it%20that%20creates%20a%20huge%20issue%20for%20the%20planet%20and%20the%20natural%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20Ahuja%2C%20architect-turned-entrepreneur%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98Sereno%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20out%20of%20Amritsar%20with%20a%20design%20office%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Yuvraj%20is%20making%20the%20best%20use%20of%20plastic%20trimmings%20and%20everyday%20plastics%20by%20converting%20them%20into%20100%25%20recyclable%20planters%20and%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20architect%20to%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%20in%20the%20family%20business.%20His%20father%20had%20established%20Frontier%20Polymers%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20in%201990%2C%20manufacturing%20rotomoulded%20products%20like%20water%20tanks%20and%20household%20plastic%20items.%20As%20the%20only%20son%2C%20Yuvraj%20joined%20the%20bu