%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Yuvraj%E2%80%99s%20design%20instincts%20nudged%20him%20in%20another%20direction.%20The%20turning%20point%20came%20when%20his%20mother%20brought%20home%20a%20few%20cheap%20plastic%20pots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%2C%20how%20can%20we%20create%20a%20better%20version%20in%20terms%20of%20design%20and%20durability%3F%E2%80%9D%20This%20question%20sparked%20the%20birth%20of%20Sereno%20in%202013%2C%20initially%20focusing%20on%20high-quality%2C%20beautifully%20designed%20planters%20and%20seats%20made%20from%20virgin%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20Sereno%20won%20the%20CIA%20Design%20Excellence%20Award%2C%20a%20prestigious%20recognition%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Interior%20Designers%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20Japan.%20The%20company%20also%20picked%20up%20three%20European%20design%20awards%2C%20a%20sure%20sign%20of%20its%20strong%20design%20ethos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20virgin%20plastic%20to%20repurposed%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20years%2C%20sustainability%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20priority.%20%E2%80%9CPlastic%20was%20the%20mode%20of%20manufacturing%20in%202013%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yuvraj%20explains.%20But%20the%20shift%20came%20gradually.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsereno.co.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBy%202018%2C%20Sereno%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20tapping%20into%20its%20own%20factory%20waste%2C%20trimmings%2C%20and%20rejections%2C%20which%20used%20to%20end%20up%20unused%2C%20to%20make%20planters%2C%20aligning%20more%20closely%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20reuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%