2%80%99t%20real%20(hallucinations)%2C%20holding%20false%20beliefs%20(delusions)%2C%20confused%20thinking%2C%20and%20unusual%20or%20unpredictable%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYears%20later%2C%20when%20I%20was%20doing%20my%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20psychology%2C%20I%20came%20across%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98catatonia%E2%80%99%20(a%20state%20where%20a%20person%20may%20appear%20awake%20but%20is%20unresponsive%20or%20immobile).%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20it%20clicked.%20That%20night%20on%20the%20sofa%20was%20one%20of%20her%20first%20symptoms%20of%20schizophrenia%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20many%20I%20would%20come%20to%20recognise%2C%20but%20none%20quite%20as%20haunting%20as%20that%20moment%20when%20she%20was%20right%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20completely%20gone%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mahira.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-51_11zon-1748415710.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-51_11zon-1748415710.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-51_11zon-1748415710-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-51_11zon-1748415710-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-51_11zon-1748415710-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-51_11zon-1748415710-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440212%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchizophrenia%20is%20a%20severe%20mental%20disorder%20that%20affects%20how%20a%20person%20thinks%2C%20feels%2C%20and%20behaves.%20Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20their%20mother%20became%20absorbed%20in%20Naina%E2%80%99s%20care%2C%20Mahira%20quietly%20took%20on%20more%20than%20her%20share.%20From%20school%20runs%20to%20helping%20younger%20siblings%20study%2C%20she%20stepped%20into%20responsibility%20without%20being%20asked%20%E2%80%94%20and%20continued%20to%20shoulder%20it%20for%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20as%20if%20her%20life%20depended%20on%20it.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20it%20as%20caregiving%20back%20then%3B%20it%20was%20just%20what%20needed%20to%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahira%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20time%20I%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20think%20about%20having%20a%20family%20of%20my%20own%2C%20I%20had%20already%20raised%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Naina%20was%20the%20one%20with%20the%20diagnosis%2C%20schizophrenia%20consumed%20the%20entire%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20rocky%20road%20to%20a%20diagnosis%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20Naina%20would%20claim%20to%20hear%20and%20see%20things%20and%20would%20isolate%20herself%20at%20times.%20But%20things%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%20after%20two%20stressful%20events%20in%20her%20personal%20life%20pushed%20her%20to%20the%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shaji%20S%2C%20Chief%20Psychiatrist%20at%20Bethesda%20Hospital%2